sub_title:
Manager Research BV, 
University Medical Center Groningen
summary:
You've got a dream? I'll help you to make it happen. 

A results-driven and determined policy advisor, project manager and development practitioner with international programme management experience, excellent interpersonal skills and an exceptionally positive attitude. Overcomes challenges through a tenacious and questioning approach, innovates and makes things happen. 

Specialties: Programme and project management, policy analysis, gender equality, advisory services, advocacy, resource mobilization, coordination, contract negotiation, knowledge management, public private partnerships and participative approach.
